# http://data.org/615001032/2025-26/didactic_resource/1
<http://data.org/615001032/2025-26/didactic_resource/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
